sentences.english: The Voyage of Captain Woodes Rogers, round the world.

sentences.english: They have performed really, really well, ' according to buying director Holli Rogers.

sentences.english: The Packers' coach has said Aaron Rodgers will be the starter.

sentences.english: Rogers is reputed to have been a very gifted clinician.

sentences.english: The photo shows Rogers with Mr. Jeffery Leng , Resident Manager of Sofitel Galaxy Nanjing.

sentences.english: Rhona Rogers had been friends with Sally Thompson for more than 20 years.

sentences.english: Coach Rogers and Lue stepped in and helped with some of the drills.

sentences.english: Shoham and Rogers believe that ice provides a perfect explanation.

sentences.english: Once they had left Key Biscayne, Rogers and Laird quickly reversed themselves.

sentences.english: Humour is learned behaviour, Mr Rodgers says.

sentences.english: It was unlikely that we should become confidants while rogers was in retirement.

sentences.english: Mr Rogers will do duty for me while I'm away next week.
sentences.chinese: 下週我外出時，羅傑斯先生代我履行職務。

sentences.english: He is now the chairman of Rogers Holdings.
sentences.chinese: 他現在是羅傑斯控股的主席。

sentences.english: Arby's and Hardy's have 7 times as much fat as Roy Roger's.

sentences.english: The manservant, Rogers, cleared his throat and passed his tongue over his dry lips.
